text: Claudiu Florin Juncănaru (born 18 February 1996) is a Romanian professional footballer who plays as a midfielder for Liga III side CSM Focșani.Liga 3 / Constantinescu a adus victoria lui Turris Oltul Turnu Magurele in etapa de azi. Urmeaza meciul de cupa cu CS Balotesti si apoi derby-ul cu Municipal Brasov. teresport.ro ==Honours== ;Turris Turnu Măgurele *Liga III: 2018–19 ==References== ==External links== * Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Romanian footballers Category:Association football midfielders Category:Liga I players Category:Liga II players Category:FC Botoșani players Category:FC Farul Constanța players Category:AFC Turris-Oltul Turnu Măgurele players Category:CSM Focșani players
